prodNameC: 羅氏可霸斯免疫分析三碘甲狀腺素檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagents - working solutions
M    Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 1 bottle, 12 mL:       Streptavidin-coated microparticles 0.72 mg/mL; preservative.
R1   Anti-T3-Ab~Ru(bpy) (gray cap), 1 bottle, 16 mL: Polyclonal anti-T3-antibody (sheep) labeled with ruthenium complex 75 ng/mL; ANS 0.8 mg/mL; phosphate buffer       100 mmol/L, pH 7.4; preservative.
R2   T3~biotin (black cap), 1 bottle, 16 mL: Biotinylated T3 3 ng/mL; ANS 0.8 mg/mL; phosphate buffer 100 mmol/L, pH 7.4; preservative.

Calset - working solutions
• T3 Cal1: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 1
• T3 Cal2: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 2
T3 in two concentration ranges (approx. 1.25 nmol/L or 0.8 ng/mL and approx. 8.5 nmol/L or 5.5 ng/mL) in a human serum matrix.
applicantName: 台灣羅氏醫療診斷設備股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區民權東路3段2號10樓
efficacy: 利用免疫分析法在體外定量檢測人類血清和血漿中的三碘甲狀腺素。
